## Group Novel
Novel related APIs.

### POST /v2/novel/bookmark/add
Add novel to bookmark.

+ Parameters
    + novel_id: `7168003` (integer, required) - Novel ID.
    + restrict: `public` (enum[string], required) - Restrict for user's accessible.
        + Members:
            + `all`
            + `public`
            + `private`
    + tags: `この素晴らしい世界に祝福を!` (string, optional) - Bookmark tag.

+ Request
    + Body

            restrict=public&novel_id=5642384

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
            }


### POST /v2/novel/bookmark/delete
Delete novel from bookmark.

+ Parameters
    + novel_id: `7168003` (integer, required) - Novel ID.
    + offset: `30` (integer, optional) - Offset index.
    + include_total_comments: `true` (boolean, optional) - Including `total_comments`.

+ Request
    + Body

            novel_id=5642384

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
            }


### GET /v2/novel/bookmark/detail{?novel_id}
Get bookmark detail for specified novel.

+ Parameters
    + novel_id: `7168003` (integer, required) - Novel ID.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
